112
00:10:31,810 --> 00:10:33,510
Paus Iblis Laut Dalam.

113
00:10:37,810 --> 00:10:39,380
Kenapa tak menghindarinya?

114
00:10:40,550 --> 00:10:42,010
Anda jangan panik.

115
